		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			One of the most important spells a Necromancer  can get rather early on is the Locate Corpse spell (lets you find the corpse of target in zone).  Not only does this aid in your own body retrieval, but others will pay to have you find your bodies.<BR>
<BR>
Another point Necromancers aren't cold evil bastards like some think.  To their own kin (fellow Necs and others of similar interest) they will be kind and lend a helping hand.  I myself don't mind helping another Necromancer in need and even will help Newbies and friend find their corpse for free.<BR>
<BR>
And to close I would say this, maybe the Necromancers wouldn't hate everything else so much if all the humans and dwarves and them didn't think they were so high and mighty.  Until then Necromancers everywhere will continue to  venge their hate on those who make it rise with foolish words.
			</font>
	
		</td>
