	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Pets attack normally up to the level 8 pet. Up till then arming it with any weapon will increase its attack strength by far. At level 12 the pet gets magical attack, (with Bone Walk), and can kill magical creatures. From here on, do not arm your pet, as it will do more damage without (unless you want to sacrifice a combine wep!). Also it may not be to your advantage to tell the pet to back off if you are in for a long term conflict. Pets gain exp and levels, and so you can get a pretty hard hitting pet after it has gained a couple of levels.
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
