			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			The best weapon to use is the one with the highest damage, lowest delay, and best magical atributes.......was that a serious question?  Seeing as we're discussing necro's here....save for a Runed Totem Staff at your lower levels, it's decent for low levels, move to a Glowing Wooden Crook later on or something like that....(Water Crystal Staff, or Observer's if you're rich)  Either way....i'd stick with a staff.    Just my opinion - others would suggest a Dragoon Dirk or a Stiletto of the Bloodclaw.
